short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Redirects Fallen London Wikia/Fandom requests, and removes Fallen London Wikia/Fandom search results from Google.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Redirects Fallen London Wikia/Fandom requests to the Fallen London Wiki.

If the same page exists on the Wikia/Fandom wiki it will try to redirect to that same page on the Fallen London Wiki. Otherwise, it'll simply show the search results for that page on the Fallen London Wiki.

Note: This extension was created by the sysadmin of the Fallen London Wiki. It is not associated in any way with Fallen London, Failbetter Games, Wikia, or Fandom.

Firefox version: https://addons.mozilla.org/addon/fl-wiki-redirector

Source Code: https://github.com/alanhuang122/FLWikiRedirector

Thanks to proEndreeper for the original code. Their code can be found at: https://github.com/proEndreeper/RSWikiRedirector
